T1  - Individual Decisions Concerning the Allocation of Resources for Projects with Uncertain Consequences
AU  - Berg, Claus C.
Y1  - 1974/09/01
PY  - 1974
DA  - 1974/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.21.1.98
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.21.1.98
